decks.notes: This deck focuses on utilizing the graveyard as a resource with the commander Karador, Ghost Chieftain at the helm. It includes a combination of creatures that can be easily recurred from the graveyard, such as creatures with enter-the-battlefield and sacrifice effects, along with cards like Birthing Pod and Survival of the Fittest to tutor for key pieces. The deck also includes various combo pieces like Reveillark and Karmic Guide to create powerful synergies and finish off opponents. The goal is to set up a board state where you can quickly assemble your combo pieces and overwhelm your opponent with a flurry of powerful creatures and disruptive interactions.
